# Game Creator

Players can create games.

Two methods:

## AI Builder

Player simply describes the game.

Example:

"I want a 4-player funny obstacle game."

AI automatically generates:

- Map
- Rules
- Obstacles
- Rewards

---

## Manual Builder

Players build everything themselves.

Features:

- Drag & Drop
- Copy
- Paste
- Delete
- Rotate
- Resize
- Undo
- Redo

Everything is designed to be extremely easy.

Even young children should be able to build games.

---

# AI Assistant

Manual Builder includes an AI Assist button.

Examples:

"Add jungle."

"Add obstacles."

"Add trees."

"Decorate this room."

AI creates the requested objects.

Players simply drag them into position.

